SALI Viewer

This is an application to generate and explore SALI networks and SALI
curves as described in references [1] and [2]. The code is based on
the CDK and a heavily modified version of ZGRviewer (0.8.0).

Building
--------

To build the SALI viewer jar file, run 

> ant sali

You should see a file called sali.jar in the current directory. To see
other available targets, run 

> ant info


